segments.text: A little boy is getting himself some cookies out of the jar, and the stool is turning over on him that he's standing on.
He's handing the little girl some cookies out of the jar.
Well, that's in the first one.
He's handing the little girl cookies out of the cookie jar, and he's on the stool, and it's turning over, and he's handing her some cookies.
And in the second picture, the little girl looks as though she's drying dishes, and the sink is running over on the floor.
